title: Aladdin's Eatery
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegan choices include lentil soup, veggie chili, v-9 vegetable soup, hummus, baba, tabouli, pita, falafel (not fried in oil with meat), grape leaves, mujadara, loubie plate and jasmine's favorite. There are also juices and fruit smoothies (w/out milk) and a jam cookie and blueberry bar (labeled vegan on the menu).
